<section class="hero"><div class="container">
<div class="label">Fifth Circuit · Louisiana</div>
<h1>United States Bankruptcy Court for the Eastern District of Louisiana</h1>
<p class="subtitle">United States Bankruptcy Court for the Eastern District of Louisiana has processed 178,422 federal bankruptcy filings in the Federal Judicial Center Integrated Database, ranking 67th of 94 US bankruptcy districts by total case volume, with Chapter 13 accounting for 71.56% of classified filings.</p>
<div class="datastamp">Data updated <time datetime="2026-04-21">2026-04-21</time>. <a href="/research/methodology/">Methodology &amp; sources</a>.</div>
</div></section>
<main class="container">
<div class="breadcrumb"><a href="/">Home</a><span class="sep">/</span><a href="/cases/">Cases</a><span class="sep">/</span>E.D. La.</div>
<div class="stat-grid"><div class="stat-cell"><span class="v">178,422</span><span class="k">Total cases (FJC IDB)</span></div><div class="stat-cell"><span class="v">5,240</span><span class="k">FY 2025 filings</span></div><div class="stat-cell"><span class="v">71.56%</span><span class="k">Chapter 13 share</span></div><div class="stat-cell"><span class="v">27.09%</span><span class="k">Chapter 7 share</span></div><div class="stat-cell"><span class="v">20.36%</span><span class="k">Prior-filer rate (Ch 13)</span></div><div class="stat-cell"><span class="v">0.0%</span><span class="k">RECAP coverage</span></div></div><p class="datastamp">National rank: <strong>67th of 94</strong> by total case volume (30th percentile). See all rankings below.</p>
<section id="filings">
<h2><span class="label">Section 01</span>Filing Volume</h2>
<p>Annual federal bankruptcy filings in E.D. La., FY 2010–2026. The most recent fiscal year is rendered with a muted marker to indicate its incomplete status.</p>
